Tasks available:
    all-string --> prints all items in table
    first-string --> prints first item in table
    last-string --> prints last item in table
    specific-integer --> input number for specific item from table at position given
            by 4 means number 4 in the list; 4 = 4 not 4 = 3
    search --> input word for output all items with word contained

Variables:
    con --> connection to database
    cur --> cursor for connection

